---
globs: *.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

do not create barrel files
do not add code with the keyword `void` to run async code within synchronous contexts. use async or effect
do not create `export *`. explicitly name the exports

prefer `undefined` over null unless the server response requires/includes nulls.
prefer `undefined` over empty string

prefer map/filter over loops and conditionals
avoid array and object mutation
